channel.title: PI starter base & DELTA starter base
channel.description:
Hello, I want to code a 2006 rsps and I searched for a PI base. Problem 1. :I found this PI base http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,495936.0.html Everything works except the server source. It gives me over 150 errors. Every error has to do with "apache.mina" I don't know what it is and where to get it :/ (Example: import org.apache.mina.common.IoAcceptor;)
'Problem 2': I searched for a cleaned (nothing added) delta source with client. I found a good client, but there are no editable .java files. I found another delta base for the server but there was too much crap in that :( Anyone knows where i can download a CLEAN delta source + client? (Yes i used google but found only shit)
Please help me. Send a new link or help me with the errors
